data.description: Welcome home! NEW ROOF installed December 2023!!! This beautiful home features detailed crown molding through out, detailed wood work in formal dining room and around feature windows, high ceilings plus a cozy wood burning fireplace. Gorgeous ceramic wood flooring in foyer and formal dining. The spacious kitchen offers a breakfast bar and eat in kitchen area. Large primary suite with separate shower and whirlpool tub. Enjoy a quiet evening while sitting under your pergola in the private fenced yard. 10 minutes from the interstate and the beach, 15 minutes from Keesler Air Force Base, shopping and entertainment!
